text: RT @ABC: JUST IN: A study of more than 96,000 coronavirus patients in hospitals around the world found those treated with chloroquine or hydroxychloroquine had a considerably higher risk of death than those who did not receive the antimalarial drugs. https://t.co/Kt52mvgeWC
